      e) In the interest of preventing theft, fraud, or otherwise malicious activity, the copyright holder
         retains the right to revoke this permission from individuals or entities at any time.

The above permissions and exemptions do not apply to files prominently noted as being exempt from these permissions
or are held under a different license.
